# Rakkib Machine Rules

This machine follows Rakkib standards.

Before making any infrastructure change, read `{{DATA_ROOT}}/README.md`.

Rules:
- backups first
- one issue at a time
- never serve from a source directory
- keep secrets in `.env` files, not compose files
- do not rotate `N8N_ENCRYPTION_KEY` after first use
- do not rotate `AUTHENTIK_SECRET_KEY` after first use
